    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nNeovim's colorscheme looks worse than helix's inside Linux tty, here is a comparison (neovim using default colorscheme on left, helix with shipped base16_transparent colorscheme on right, both have treesitter enabled)\r\n\r\n![tty_neovim_helix](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/assets/76579810/55c10592-459e-40ff-a323-5c25c76c8d4f)\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nNeovim's default colorscheme should be as informative as helix's.",
    "closed_at": "2023-12-29T20:16:48Z",
