            "body": "I'll also add that I think the premise of the issue is questionable:\r\n\r\n>Neovim's default colorscheme should be as informative as helix's.\r\n\r\nThis is a subjective judgment. Personally, I find the explosion of colors in the Helix screenshot to have very little informational content.\r\n\r\nNo single colorscheme can possibly please everyone, which is why both Neovim and Helix package many choices.",
