            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Alright, I like Neovim's default colorscheme, just to make sure it is intended to be plain and minimal.\r\n\r\nCould we change hl-Comment and hl-NormalFloat in the default colorscheme, specifically using silver/grey for comments and a light background for floating windows, this will make comments and floating window more distinguishable in tty, the following is some comparisons (original default colorscheme on the right):\r\n\r\n![tty_neovim_default_colorscheme_00](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/assets/76579810/4f13df9e-087f-4adf-a12c-ea09a20cb370)\r\n\r\nComments in silver vs comments in white\r\n\r\n![tty_neovim_default_colorscheme_01](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/assets/76579810/a18c16e8-a98b-4675-8c5c-f6eaaa65a821)\r\n\r\nLSP hover window with light & dark background\r\n",
